  "text": "According to the results, total innovation intensity of the agri-food sector is greater than the average of all the sectors of the VC. Both components, direct and indirect innovation intensities, are greater in the agrifood sector than in the average of other sectors as it is shown in Table 1 . These results would refute the generally accepted idea that the agri-food sector is scarcely innovative (see for example [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Besides, it is worth to highlight the capacity of agri-food sector of the VC to induce innovation in the own region compared to the whole Valencian economy. From this perspective, the agrifood sector would be strategic for the territory as it induces more innovation in the region than the rest of the sectors.",
